1. *Posvuda* su videli policajci (Everywhere the police officers saw).
2. U kući je *posvuda* bilo prljavo (There was dirt *everywhere* in the house).
3. *Posvuda* su se čuli zvuci grada (Sounds of the city could be heard *all around*).
4. Iako nije bilo vidljivo, *posvuda* je bilo sitnog peska (Although it wasn't visible, there was fine sand *everywhere*).
5. Kada je padao sneg, *posvuda* je bilo bele boje (When it was snowing, *everywhere* was white).
6. Ljudi su se okupljali *posvuda* oko pozornice (People gathered *everywhere* around the stage).
7. Deca su razbacala igračke *posvuda* po sobi (Children scattered toys *everywhere* in the room).
8. *Posvuda* se čulo cvrkutanje ptica (Bird chirping could be heard *everywhere*).
9. Trgovci su nudili svoju robu *posvuda* po pijaci (Merchants offered their goods *everywhere* at the market).
10. *Posvuda* je vladao haos (Chaos reigned *everywhere*).

Note: *Posvuda* means "everywhere" in Serbian.